metadata.name: Endless
metadata.description:
Before starting this journey of art, Iceman always thought of himself as a terrible artist. Had zero confidence in any of the "art" I would make. 
It wasn't until a close friend on twitter challenged me to create something every day for 40 days straight that I really understood the power of creativity.  

This will be my first ever piece of art that I created on the blockchain.  
Its titled " Endless " , because after making art for 31 days in a row, Iceman has realized that Art, Creativity and everything that goes along with those two things are completely "ENDLESS".

Don't be afraid to try something new. Don't be afraid to walk through the darkness.
